com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.deser

Class DefaultDeserializationContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.DatabindContext
      • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.DeserializationContext
        • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.deser.DefaultDeserializationContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultDeserializationContext.Impl

    public abstract class DefaultDeserializationContext
extends DeserializationContext
implements java.io.Serializable
    Complete DeserializationContext implementation that adds extended API for ObjectMapper (and ObjectReader) to call, as well as implements certain parts that base class has left abstract. The remaining abstract methods (createInstance(com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.DeserializationConfig, com.fasterxml.jackson.core.JsonParser, com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.InjectableValues), with(com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.deser.DeserializerFactory)) are left so that custom implementations will properly implement them to return intended subtype.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
